text: Taeniesthes is a genus of scarab beetles.Biolib ==Species== * Taeniesthes collinsi Allard, 1992 \- Ethiopia * Taeniesthes picturata (Harold, 1878) * Taeniesthes specularis Gerstaecker, 1867 \- Kenya and Tanzania Entomologi ItalianiGlobal Names ==Distribution== This genus is widespread in eastern Africa (Ethiopia, Kenya, Tanzania). ==References== Category:Cetoniinae
